Package: gmrfs
Type: Package
Title: Adaptive GMRF Models for INLA via cgeneric
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Esmail", "Abdul Fattah",
           email = "esmail.abdulfattah@kaust.edu.sa",
           role  = c("aut", "cre"))
  )
Description: Wraps four adaptive Gaussian Markov random field models -
    fbesag (Besag with partitioned precisions), collapsed, partial, and
    stacked block models - exposed to R-INLA through its cgeneric
    interface. When INLA ships a precompiled library for a given model
    (via inla.external.lib), that copy is preferred; otherwise the
    package's own compiled shared library is used.
License: GPL (>= 2)
Encoding: UTF-8
Depends:
    R (>= 4.0)
Imports:
    INLA,
    Matrix
Additional_repositories: https://inla.r-inla-download.org/R/stable
URL: https://github.com/esmail-abdulfattah/gmrfs
BugReports: https://github.com/esmail-abdulfattah/gmrfs/issues
Config/roxygen2/version: 8.0.0
